ruments, graphic designer (2016\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jaxsta.com/recording/04144f94-c2ee-4b7b-a644-f38f20886444/overview|title=Open Your Mind (feat. Andrew Williams)|website=www.jaxsta.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://jaxsta.com/recording/04144f94-c2ee-4b7b-a644-f38f20886444/overview|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Adrian Cogen \u2013 dancer (2016\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Suzanne Vuegen \u2013 dancer (2016\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n\n; Albums\n\n* ''The Early Years''  2016  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191061029427)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gravitynoir.com/dashboard/pages/videos_90s|title=Gravity Noir The early years|last=Gravity|first=Noir|date=2015-11-10|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* ''Handmade''  2016  (CD Baby/Indieplant/Gravity Productions UPC 0680596923527)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7BRUG7fgQfA&list=OLAK5uy_kGxBjMk__4DeDCTrnNz1qI0LTEpjXNz7M|title=Gravity Noir Handmade|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|title=Gravity Noir|last=AllMusic|first=Discography|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-11-22|archive