'[[Lombardi Award]]'''\n:[[Walt Patulski]] \u2013 1971<ref name=\"LA\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rotarylombardiaward.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=blogcategory&id=25&Itemid=59 |title=Winners & Finalists |publisher=Rotary Club of Houston |accessdate=January 2, 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108234922/http://www.rotarylombardiaward.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=blogcategory&id=25&Itemid=59 |archivedate=January 8, 2009 |df=mdy }}</ref>\n:[[Ross Browner]] \u2013 1977<ref name=\"LA\" />\n:[[Chris Zorich]] \u2013 1990<ref name=\"LA\" />\n:[[Aaron Taylor (born 1972)|Aaron Taylor]] \u2013 1993<ref name=\"LA\" />\n:[[Manti Te'o]] \u2013 2012<ref name=\"LA\" />\n*'''[[Lott Trophy|Lott IMPACT Trophy]]'''\n:[[Manti Te'o]] \u2013 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/765617453/College-football-Notre-Dames-Manti-Teo-wins-Lott-Trophy.html|title=College football: Notre Dame's Manti Te'o wins Lott Trophy|date=December 9, 2012|work=DeseretNews.com|accessdate=September 6, 2015}}</ref>\n*'''[[Bronko Nagurski Trophy]]'''\n:[[Manti Te'o]] \u2013 2012<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/colleges/notre-dame-linebacker-manti-teo-wins-bronko-nagurski-award-for-nations-top-defensive-player/2012/12/03/fa5bc3a4-3db6-11e2-8a5c-473797be602c_story.html|title=Notre Dame linebacker Manti Te'o wins Bronko Nagurski Award for nation's top defensive player|date=December 3, 2012|website=The Washington Post|accessdate=December 3, 2012|df=mdy-all}}{{dead link|date=July 2018|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>\n*'''[[Outland Trophy]]'''\n:[[George Connor (American football)|George Connor]] \u2013 1946<ref name=\"OT\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sportswriters.net/fwaa/awards/outland/winners.html|title=All-Time Outland Trophy Winners|publisher=Football Writers Association of America|accessdate=January 2, 2008}}</ref>\n:[[Bill Fischer (American football)|Bill Fischer]] \u2013 1948<ref name=\"OT\" />\n:[[Ross Browne